title: Cell Phone Coverage, Haiti, 2010
name: Cell Phone Coverage, Haiti, 2010
description:
This layer shows areas with good cell phone coverage based on the Digicel Haiti map on their website. The image was downloaded, then geo-rectified using the NYPL image warper. the GeoTiff was then loaded into ArcGIS 9.3, classified down to 2 categories. i then used the raster to polygon tool and exported as the final Shapefile for upload. 

This map corresponds to the red sections of the map found on digicel's website
